## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and includes sources published up to 2025. The findings are subject to the limitations of the data sources, including potential biases in reporting and the evolving nature of the pandemic's impact. Additionally, the personal and subjective nature of some experiences may not be fully captured in quantitative data. Further research may be needed to explore long-term effects as new data becomes available.